        "name": "Write Model (Command Side)",
        "responsibility": "Handles order creation and status updates against the existing normalized 12-table schema. Emits domain events on every state change (OrderCreated, OrderStatusChanged, DeliveryCompleted, CourierAssigned). This is the existing system — minimal changes needed.",
